Nubicustos integrates with and orchestrates the following open-source security
tools. Each tool is used via its official Docker image and retains its original
license. Nubicustos does not modify these tools.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CLOUD SECURITY TOOLS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Prowler
  Repository: https://github.com/prowler-cloud/prowler
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Copyright: Prowler Cloud Security

ScoutSuite
  Repository: https://github.com/nccgroup/ScoutSuite
  License: GNU General Public License v2.0 (GPL-2.0)
  Copyright: NCC Group

  NOTE: ScoutSuite uses GPL-2.0 which requires that derivative works also be
  licensed under GPL-2.0. Since Nubicustos merely orchestrates ScoutSuite via
  Docker without modifying its source code, this does not create a derivative
  work. However, users should be aware of GPL-2.0 requirements when using
  ScoutSuite directly.

Pacu
  Repository: https://github.com/RhinoSecurityLabs/pacu
  License: BSD 3-Clause License
  Copyright: Rhino Security Labs

CloudSploit
